          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "For racing fans, particularly those who watch F1 with any level of intensity, these liveries are quite familiar. You can imagine how it feels to see the modern design applied to a cars from a few decades ago. We’re used to seeing classic liveries applied to modern road cars, like when Ford released the ",
